---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Why Choose Us - MaizeSupply Pro" description="Discover why businesses choose MaizeSupply Pro for quality assurance, reliability, fair pricing, and sustainable farmer partnerships.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1>Why Choose MaizeSupply Pro</h1>
        <p>Your trusted partner for premium maize supply with unmatched quality and service</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Overview -->
  <section class="section overview">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div class="overview-content">
          <h2>What Sets Us Apart</h2>
          <p>In a competitive market, MaizeSupply Pro stands out through our unwavering commitment to quality, reliability, and customer satisfaction. We've built our reputation on delivering exceptional service and building lasting partnerships with both farmers and businesses.</p>
          <p>Our comprehensive approach to maize supply chain management, combined with our values-driven business practices, makes us the preferred choice for companies seeking a dependable and ethical supply partner.</p>
          <div class="quick-stats">
            <div class="quick-stat">
              <span class="stat-icon">⭐</span>
              <span class="stat-text">5-Star Customer Rating</span>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-stat">
              <span class="stat-icon">🚛</span>
              <span class="stat-text">99.8% On-Time Delivery</span>
            </div>
            <div class="quick-stat">
              <span class="stat-icon">🌾</span>
              <span class="stat-text">500+ Partner Farmers</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="overview-image">
          <img src="https://images.pexels.com/photos/5647021/pexels-photo-5647021.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1260&h=750&dpr=1" alt="Quality maize and farming partnership" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Benefits -->
  <section class="section main-benefits">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Key Advantages</h2>
      <div class="benefits-grid">
        <div class="benefit-detail">
          <div class="benefit-header">
            <div class="benefit-icon">✅</div>
            <h3>Uncompromising Quality Assurance</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Our rigorous quality control process ensures you receive only the finest maize that meets or exceeds industry standards.</p>
          <div class="benefit-features">
            <h4>What This Means for You:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Multi-stage quality testing from farm to delivery</li>
              <li>Moisture content, protein level, and contamination testing</li>
              <li>Consistent grade specifications for every shipment</li>
              <li>Quality certificates and documentation</li>
              <li>Traceability to source farms</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-result">
            <strong>Result:</strong> Consistent product quality that enhances your final products and reduces waste.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-detail">
          <div class="benefit-header">
            <div class="benefit-icon">⚡</div>
            <h3>Unmatched Reliability</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Count on us for consistent supply and punctual delivery, helping you maintain smooth operations and meet your commitments.</p>
          <div class="benefit-features">
            <h4>What This Means for You:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>99.8% on-time delivery track record</li>
              <li>Backup supply sources and contingency planning</li>
              <li>Real-time tracking and communication</li>
              <li>Flexible scheduling to meet your needs</li>
              <li>Emergency supply arrangements when needed</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-result">
            <strong>Result:</strong> Peace of mind knowing your supply chain is secure and dependable.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-detail">
          <div class="benefit-header">
            <div class="benefit-icon">💰</div>
            <h3>Fair & Competitive Pricing</h3>
          </div>
          <p>Our efficient operations and direct farmer relationships enable us to offer competitive prices without compromising quality.</p>
          <div class="benefit-features">
            <h4>What This Means for You:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Volume-based pricing discounts</li>
              <li>Long-term contract pricing stability</li>
              <li>Transparent pricing with no hidden fees</li>
              <li>Market-competitive rates</li>
              <li>Seasonal pricing optimization</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-result">
            <strong>Result:</strong> Better profit margins and predictable cost structures for your business.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="benefit-detail">
          <div class="benefit-header">
            <div class="benefit-icon">🤝</div>
            <h3>Sustainable Farmer Partnerships</h3>
          </div>
          <p>We support local farming communities through fair trade practices and sustainable agriculture initiatives.</p>
          <div class="benefit-features">
            <h4>What This Means for You:</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Ethically sourced maize from verified farmers</li>
              <li>Support for sustainable farming practices</li>
              <li>Community development initiatives</li>
              <li>Fair pricing for farmers ensuring supply continuity</li>
              <li>Positive brand association with ethical sourcing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="benefit-result">
            <strong>Result:</strong> Enhanced brand reputation and contribution to sustainable agriculture.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Service Excellence -->
  <section class="section service-excellence">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Service Excellence</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-3">
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">📞</div>
          <h3>Dedicated Support Team</h3>
          <p>Personal account managers provide ongoing support, quick response to inquiries, and proactive communication about your orders and deliveries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🔄</div>
          <h3>Flexible Solutions</h3>
          <p>Customized packaging, delivery schedules, and service arrangements tailored to your specific business requirements and operational needs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">📊</div>
          <h3>Market Intelligence</h3>
          <p>Regular market updates, price forecasts, and supply chain insights help you make informed decisions and plan effectively.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
          <h3>Risk Management</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive insurance coverage, backup suppliers, and contingency plans protect your business from supply chain disruptions.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">📱</div>
          <h3>Technology Integration</h3>
          <p>Modern tracking systems, digital documentation, and automated communication keep you informed throughout the supply process.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="service-feature">
          <div class="feature-icon">🌱</div>
          <h3>Sustainability Focus</h3>
          <p>Environmental responsibility through sustainable practices, efficient transportation, and support for eco-friendly farming methods.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitive Comparison -->
  <section class="section competitive-comparison">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">How We Compare</h2>
      <div class="comparison-table">
        <div class="table-header">
          <div class="feature-column">Features</div>
          <div class="us-column">MaizeSupply Pro</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">Typical Competitors</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Quality Testing</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ Multi-stage testing</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">❌ Basic testing only</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Delivery Reliability</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ 99.8% on-time</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">⚠️ 85-90% typical</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Farmer Relationships</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ Direct partnerships</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">❌ Broker networks</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Customer Support</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ Dedicated managers</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">❌ Call center only</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Packaging Options</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ Fully customizable</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">⚠️ Limited options</div>
        </div>
        <div class="table-row">
          <div class="feature-column">Transparency</div>
          <div class="us-column">✅ Full traceability</div>
          <div class="competitor-column">❌ Limited visibility</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Client Testimonials -->
  <section class="section testimonials">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What Our Clients Say</h2>
      <div class="testimonials-grid">
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <p>"MaizeSupply Pro has transformed our supply chain. Their consistent quality and reliable delivery have allowed us to focus on our core business while knowing our maize supply is in excellent hands."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-avatar">👨‍💼</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <strong>Michael Derrick</strong>
              <span>Operations Director, Kirinyaga Food Processing</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <p>"The team at MaizeSupply Pro goes above and beyond. Their customer service is exceptional, and they've helped us optimize our inventory management through their flexible delivery options."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-avatar">👩‍💼</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <strong>Sarah cherop</strong>
              <span>Procurement Manager, Metro Wholesale</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonial">
          <div class="testimonial-content">
            <p>"Working with MaizeSupply Pro has given us peace of mind. Their commitment to quality and sustainability aligns perfectly with our company values and customer expectations."</p>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial-author">
            <div class="author-avatar">👨‍🍳</div>
            <div class="author-info">
              <strong>James Kariuki</strong>
              <span>CEO, Organic Foods Co.</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Call to Action -->
  <section class="section cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h2>Experience the MaizeSupply Pro Difference</h2>
        <p>Join hundreds of satisfied clients who have made the smart choice. Let us show you why we're the preferred maize supply partner.</p>
        <div class="cta-buttons">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Today</a>
          <a href="tel:+15551234567" class="btn btn-secondary">Speak to Our Team</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    color: white;
    padding: 120px 0 80px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .hero-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .overview {
    background: white;
  }

  .overview-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .overview-content p {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .quick-stats {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .quick-stat {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 15px;
    background: #f0fdf4;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
  }

  .stat-icon {
    font-size: 1.5rem;
  }

  .stat-text {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #166534;
  }

  .overview-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 450px;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .main-benefits {
    background: #f9fafb;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(400px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .benefit-detail {
    background: white;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .benefit-detail:hover {
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  .benefit-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefit-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .benefit-header h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .benefit-detail p {
    color: #6b7280;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .benefit-features h4 {
    color: #1f2937;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .benefit-features ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .benefit-features li {
    padding: 5px 0 5px 20px;
    color: #4b5563;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit-features li::before {
    content: "✓";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: #22c55e;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .benefit-result {
    background: #f0fdf4;
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #166534;
  }

  .service-excellence {
    background: white;
  }

  .service-feature {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    background: #f9fafb;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .service-feature:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .feature-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .service-feature h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .service-feature p {
    color: #6b7280;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .competitive-comparison {
    background: #f9fafb;
  }

  .comparison-table {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
  }

  .table-header {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    background: #1f2937;
    color: white;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .table-header > div {
    padding: 20px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .table-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
  }

  .table-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .table-row > div {
    padding: 15px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .feature-column {
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #1f2937;
  }

  .us-column {
    justify-content: center;
    background: #f0fdf4;
    color: #166534;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .competitor-column {
    justify-content: center;
    color: #6b7280;
  }

  .testimonials {
    background: white;
  }

  .testimonials-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 30px;
  }

  .testimonial {
    background: #f9fafb;
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .testimonial:hover {
    background: white;
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    transform: translateY(-3px);
  }

  .testimonial-content {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .testimonial-content p {
    color: #4b5563;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
  }

  .testimonial-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 15px;
  }

  .author-avatar {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  .author-info strong {
    color: #1f2937;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .author-info span {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cta {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    color: white;
  }

  .cta-content {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .cta-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* Responsive Design */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .overview-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .benefits-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .overview-image img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .table-header,
    .table-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .table-header > div,
    .table-row > div {
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
    }

    .table-header > div:first-child,
    .table-row > div:first-child {
      background: #f9fafb;
      font-weight: 600;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .hero-content h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }

    .benefit-detail {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .quick-stats {
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>